<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- وَظِلٍّ نَافِعٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَتَحْتَ شَجَرَةٍ عَلَيْهَا ثَمَرٌ يُقْصَدُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> وَاسْتِقْبَالُ قِبْلَةٍ وَاسْتِدْبَارُهَا بِفَضَاءٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
