<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- وَالسِّوَاكُ مَسْنُونٌ مُطْلَقًا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> إِلَّا لِصَائِمٍ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> بَعْدَ الزَّوَالِ فَيُكْرَهُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَيُبَاحُ قَبْلَهُ بِعُودٍ رَطْبٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> وَيُسْتَحَبُّ بِيَابِسٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَلَمْ يُصِبِ السُّنّةَ مَنِ اسْتَاكَ بِغَيْرِ عُودٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
